From fighting in protests, to fighting for your position as the first black woman in our little town working next to the mayor! Granny all I’ve ever seen you do is fight, and you’ve installed that fight in me! I’ll never give up on anything because of you. I’m thankful we got to spend soo many years together. But God needed his best fighter next to him. 
Until we meet again, rest up. love you Grandma V ✊🏾🕊
